info.title: Cisco-IOS-XE-appqoe-sslproxy-oper
info.description:
This module contains a collection of YANG definitions
     of SSL proxy operational data for Application Quality
     of Experience (APPQOE). This includes SSL proxy configuration,
     status and statistics.
     Copyright (c) 2020-2022 by Cisco Systems, Inc.
     All rights reserved.

Cisco IOS-XE operational state data (read-only).

**Paths:** 3
